OL,3,CValdo Calocane kicked officer after
OL,4,Ckilling three people, inquiry hears
OL,6,FTriple killer Valdo Calocane kicked a
OL,7,Fdetention officer when he was brought
OL,8,Finto custody after he fatally stabbed
OL,9,Fthree people and ran over three others
OL,10,Fwith a van in Nottingham, the inquiry
OL,11,Finto the attacks has heard.
OL,13,FCalocane was taken to the city's
OL,14,Fcustody suite, where he repeatedly
OL,15,Fswore at a sergeant, after going on a
OL,16,Fviolent rampage in the early hours of
OL,17,FJune 13, 2023.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
