OL,3,CValdo Calocane kicked officer after
OL,4,Ckilling three people, inquiry hears
OL,6,FThe public inquiry, which is being
OL,7,Fheld in central London, was shown
OL,8,Ffootage on Tuesday of officers helping
OL,9,FCalocane, who was handcuffed, out of a
OL,10,Fpolice van and telling him to "mind
OL,11,Fyour head" on the roof of the vehicle.
OL,13,FThe video showed Calocane, who was
OL,14,Fdiagnosed with paranoid schizophrenia
OL,15,Fin 2020, pause for a moment before he
OL,16,Fstruck out with his leg out towards a
OL,17,Ffemale officer and was then restrained
OL,18,Fon the floor.
OL,26,@rD@_OUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
