OL,3,CValdo Calocane kicked officer after
OL,4,Ckilling three people, inquiry hears
OL,6,FIn the hours before, Calocane had
OL,7,Ffatally stabbed University of
OL,8,FNottingham undergraduates Barnaby
OL,9,FWebber and Grace O'Malley-Kumar, both
OL,10,F19, in Ilkeston Road, Nottingham, and
OL,11,F65-year-old Ian Coates in Magdala
OL,12,FRoad, before driving at three other
OL,13,Fpeople.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
