OL,3,CValdo Calocane kicked officer after
OL,4,Ckilling three people, inquiry hears
OL,6,FAsked about the assault at the custody
OL,7,Fsuite, Chief Inspector Lisa Murray, of
OL,8,FNottinghamshire Police, told the
OL,9,Finquiry: "I think from the extent of
OL,10,F(the officer's) response and reaction,
OL,11,Fit came as a shock and certainly I
OL,12,Fthink she goes on to describe that in
OL,13,Fher statement.
OL,15,F"So it wasn't anticipated."
OL,26,@qD@JOUwD@AOUwD@[O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
