OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773846665
OL,3,CValdo Calocane kicked officer after
OL,4,Ckilling three people, inquiry hears
OL,6,FThe inquiry has previously heard how
OL,7,FCalocane headbutted, punched and swung
OL,8,Fhandcuffs at a police officer who was
OL,9,Ftrying to detain him under mental
OL,10,Fhealth laws nearly two years before
OL,11,Fthe attacks, on September 3 2021,
OL,12,Fcausing swelling to his face.
OL,14,FThe inquiry was shown footage of
OL,15,FCalocane at the booking desk on the
OL,16,Fmorning of the killings with officers
OL,17,Fon each side, when the custody
OL,18,Fsergeant asked: "What's your name
OL,19,Fmate? Are you going to speak to me?"
OL,21,FCalocane replied: "**** off."
OL,26,@zD@QOU{D@dO]}D@SOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
