CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773846665
OL,3,CValdo Calocane kicked officer after
OL,4,Ckilling three people, inquiry hears
OL,6,FAfter explaining that her role was to
OL,7,Fcare for him in custody, the sergeant
OL,8,Fthen asked Calocane: "Can I have your
OL,9,Fsurname?", to which he said: "****
OL,10,Foff".
OL,12,FIn custody, when asked whether he
OL,13,Fexperienced hallucinations or voices,
OL,14,FCalocane said: "I do not want to
OL,15,Fdiscuss that with you", the inquiry
OL,16,Fheard.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@IO]qD@^OUrD@DO]vD@POUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
