CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1773846665
OL,3,CValdo Calocane kicked officer after
OL,4,Ckilling three people, inquiry hears
OL,6,FMs Murray told the inquiry that
OL,7,FCalocane refused to have medical
OL,8,Fsamples taken from him and only
OL,9,Fanswered some questions asked by
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FShe said: "Some information that he
OL,13,Fwas asked about himself, and that
OL,14,Fwasn't necessarily about the
OL,15,Foffending, he seemed to be more
OL,16,Fcomfortable answering.
OL,18,F"But there was certainly a lack of
OL,19,Fanswer and engagement when it was
OL,20,Fevidential material that was put to
OL,21,Fhim."
OL,26,@tD@KOUzD@AOU}D@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
